Click on Blacklist tags and there will be a bunch of tag categories such as: Tags, Artists, and Parodies, with a little + symbol next to them. Click on the + corresponding to the type of tag you want to block and than type the name of the tag. It should give you an autocomplete option so click on the result that you want to block.
After you've added any tags you wish to blacklist, simply click the Save button at the bottom of the page and you're done! You will no longer see hentai with blacklisted tags in the Popular Now section of the front page, and search results with blacklisted tags will appear greyed out.
